title: Buffy The Vampire Slayer : Done and Dusted (Soundtrack)
description:
A fan made soundtrack I compiled together from the hit TV show "Buffy The Vampire Slayer" the album consists mostly of Indie/Rock music as it is the type of music I mainly listen too, but I have thrown in a few ballads too.

Tracklisting :-

1. Velvet Chain - Buffy

2. Stretch Princess - Universe

3. Louie Says - She

4. 3 Day Wheely - Rotten Apples

5. Trespassers William - I Know

6. Clement & Murray (Featuring Cari Howe) - Anything

7. Mellonova - Hi Dee Ho

8. Cracker - The Good Life

9. Headland - Sweet Charlotte Rose

10. THC (Shy) - Need to Destroy

11. Aberdeen - Cities and Buses

12. Virgil - Heal Yourself

13. Bush - Out of This World

14. Clement & Murray - Wolves

15. Heather Nova - It's Only Love

16. Four Star Mary (Dingoes Ate My Baby) - Fate

17. The Breeders - Buffy Theme

Enjoy !
